title: Nothing show up in when trying to refund
body:
Hello! Im purchased ezreal for rp for around 2-3 Months ago. Its not stansning something about champ but i can see that IT stands 3 refunds remain. So i need help! Anybody else WHO got this?
Joshua

replies.body: Hey Bert-Jeff-Joshi!  I looked into this for you, and it doesn't look like that particular refund is eligible.  Per our[ refund guidelines](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201751864-Content-Refund-FAQ), in addition to refund tokens the purchase has to also be within 90 days.  Items beyond that can no longer be refunded.  Let me know if that helps clear things up!
